title: Support the DAO's migration?
body:
The original proposal can be found on the forum. The first and only comment added by the original poster contains the specific details for which the proposal is being voted on. Vote yes if you agree with every detail of the document and vote no if you disagree with any part of it. If you vote no, please address the specific areas you disagree with so that we may address these concerns and hold another vote if needed.

https://forum.yape.exchange/t/mint-a-new-yape-token-to-replace-the-token-trinity-migrate-dao-treasury-and-reserves-to-daohaus/62/3
